  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Applied Solar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Applied Solar Technologies (AST or the Company) is a solar PV based off-grid power solution company that provides off grid solar power currently to telecom towers which often rely on diesel based generation for 50  100% of their power requirements. AST builds and operates these solar installations and takes over the power supply management of each site. It uses a combination of solar PV, battery back-up and diesel generator making it a hybrid energy solution that optimizes the usage of various sources through a controller. The optimal usage of these sources results in decreased diesel consumption, increased battery life and reduced diesel generator maintenance and replacement costs resulting in savings for ASTs consumers.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project will have strong development impact by way of development of off-grid renewable energy through solar power. It will contribute to climate change mitigation by reduced use of diesel fuel which has detrimental environmental effects. Further, the Project will result in employment opportunities during both implementation and operations in remote areas. It will also contribute to government revenues by way of taxes and reduced use of subsidized diesel fuel.</narrative>
  </description>
